ListGraph
public interface Graph<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends Cloneable<Graph<NodeType,EdgeType>>, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, java.io.Serializable

Declares the whole functionality of a single typed graph.

Its edges can be directed or undirected.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
